  "description": {
    "main": "Transform your living room into a movie theatre with the Sony BRAVIA Theatre Bar 6. Its immersive 3.1.2 channel surround sound makes you feel like you're right in the middle of the action. Perfect for high-octane thrillers or nail-biting horror flicks. The wireless subwoofer gives you deep, rich bass and you can place it anywhere in the room. You'll feel every rumble of thunder or ominous footstep. The up-firing speakers create three-dimensional overhead sound, so there's no need for ceiling speakers. And Dolby Atmos and DTS:X technologies bring cinema-like sound to your home, making every detail come alive.",
    "goodToKnow": [
      "AI Voice Zoom 3 lets you adjust dialogue volume without changing other sounds, so you won't miss a word",
